        {
            "title": "對沖需求升溫！美元看空情緒飆10年新高 華爾街喊還會再跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nBip2aMB1S8YZL7oU986lA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/cc33c9b7428ecdd674602e1a3dea1225\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E7%9C%8B%E7%A9%BA%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E9%A3%8610%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E5%96%8A%E9%82%84%E6%9C%83%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%8C-051004795.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-17 13:53:27",
